{"tid":2400933,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Clubhouse被封  《環球時報》稱片面反华非言論自由","createTime":"2021-02-09T10:31:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-09T13:10:25.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ba83c731f70cd29b9daf653cfe38464ddaa33a43","tid":2400933,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T10:31:17.000Z","msg":"語音社群軟體Clubhouse遭中國封鎖，外媒分析指出，此舉顯示中國官方仍不願見到自由討論的風氣。不過中共官媒則持反對意見，認為平台上充斥反華的片面論述，不應稱為言論自由的天堂。<br />\n<br />\n有別於西方媒體將Clubhouse被中國封鎖視為扼殺言論自由，中國官媒環球時報英文版則稱，Clubhouse充斥反華且片面的言論，甚至有許多對中國不利的謠言流竄，不該被稱為言論自由的天堂。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://www.chinatimes .com/realtimenews/20210209003531-260409</code></pre>"},{"pid":"eaffeecf96a840f4a4608606642d0cdc3a41552e","tid":2400933,"uid":134087,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T10:41:48.000Z","msg":"片面撐华係全部人嘅自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b391aa7f9d57dc76517c78e653196b626c7d4cdc","tid":2400933,"uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T10:47:59.000Z","msg":"牆內比牆外更自由！"},{"pid":"e58c631979188606d0edc46e7046e441fcc0ff96","tid":2400933,"uid":33498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T10:48:45.000Z","msg":"南京人反皇軍非言論自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f2a8b3127b15b4203a4c9cbb3ca2272d45beae5","tid":2400933,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T10:51:45.000Z","msg":"唔夠全面<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要再加大力度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b40ea0c7555fead354a389285cbb0a76fbb3e63","tid":2400933,"uid":239384,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T10:52:41.000Z","msg":"點樣唔片面反華 要全面反華？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋乜支那代表到華咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkg